dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Sheboygan County, WI 2016
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Sheboygan County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase 'Sheboygan_Hydro_2016.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Sheboygan_HydroLine_2016' and 'Sheboygan_HydroPoly_2016'. [River and Stream lines that represent flowlines and cartographic features such as stream centerlines and river banks. Polygon features representing waterbodies.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
